    $( The closure of a subset of a topological space is the subset together
       with its limit points.  Theorem 6.6 of [Munkres] p. 97. $)
    clslp $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ S C_ X ) -> ( ( cls ` J ) ` S ) =
