    $( A subset of a topological space is closed iff it contains all its limit
       points.  Corollary 6.7 of [Munkres] p. 97. $)
    cldlp $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ S C_ X ) -> ( S e. ( Clsd ` J ) <->
